北地方法院\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　6 　　月　　28　　日\r\n                              檢  察  官  陳旭華","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PCDM/111%2c%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c1382%2c20221117%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PCDM,111,交簡,1382,20221117,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"交簡","JNO":"1382","JDATE":"20221117","JTITLE":"過失傷害"}